# install dependencies
go get github.com/stretchr/testify/assert
go get github.com/gorilla/mux
go get github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3

go mod init apis
go mod tidy
go build apis
./apis -help

# run UT
go test apis
go test -v

Extending UT:
No Global Manifest: Insert no rows into global_manifest and expect a 500 error.
Multiple Global Manifest Rows: Test with multiple rows to ensure the latest updated_at is picked (or tweak to use is_active).
Edge Cases: Test empty version strings, malformed version formats, or concurrent updates.

